overview: Holiday Rentals in Spain. Semesterbostad-Spanien.se belongs to Spain-Holiday.com. It is the newest addition to the company, which focuses on the Swedish speaking market. Semesterbostad-Spanien.se offers holiday rentals all over Spain, which more that 3500 holiday homes to choose from. There is a large variety of both villas, apartments, country homes in Spain. All properties are rented out directly from the owners, done by direkt contact from the website. Property owners may advertise their holiday home with ease through this site that is visited by thousands daily.
